  "narrative": {
    "text": "Mexico is a Latin America and the Caribbean country with a DC-type pension system centred on the Sistema de Ahorro para el Retiro \u2013 AFORE (Individual Accounts). The system includes 2 schemes: Sistema de Ahorro para el Retiro \u2013 AFORE (Individual Accounts), Pensi\u00f3n para el Bienestar de los Adultos Mayores \u2013 Non-Contributory. The normal retirement age is 65 for both men and women. Contributions total 6.3% of insurable earnings (1.1% employee, 5.1% employer).",
